00:24.232 --> 00:25.525
<i>Give this to your dad.</i>

00:25.567 --> 00:27.986
<i>-Stay away from my son.
- Titanium</i>

00:28.028 --> 00:29.029
<i>doesn't melt.</i>

00:29.070 --> 00:30.530
<i>He knows.</i>

