he's hiding anything from you.</i>

00:37.412 --> 00:39.205
<i>I'm fucked up,
and I always have been.</i>

00:39.247 --> 00:40.749
<i>I remember everything.</i>

00:40.790 --> 00:43.001
<i>Daddy will be home soon.</i>

00:43.043 --> 00:46.212
