to school that day.</i>

00:55.930 --> 00:58.391
<i>He has my Dark Passenger.</i>

00:59.601 --> 01:00.894
<i>What the fuck?!</i>

01:00.935 --> 01:02.979
<i>-Hey, psycho!
- That's enough.</i>

01:03.021 --> 01:04.981
<i>I have to tell Harrison
everything.</i>

