<i>On a hill far away</i>

01:16.076 --> 01:19.370
<i>Stood an old rugged cross</i>

01:19.412 --> 01:21.372
<i>The emblem</i>

01:21.414 --> 01:25.502
<i>Of suffering and shame</i>

01:26.711 --> 01:29.631
<i>And I love that old cross</i>

01:29.672 --> 01:31.633
<i>Hey, psycho!</i>

01:31.674 --> 01:33.593
<i>Where the dearest and best</i>

01:33.635 --> 01:35.720
<i>For a world</i>

01:35.762 --> 01:40.433
<i>Of lost sinners was slain</i>

01:40.475 --> 01:45.105
<i>And I'll cherish
the old rugged cross</i>

01:45.146 --> 01:47.774
<i>Cross</i>

01:47.816 --> 01:50.443
<i>Till my trophies</i>

01:50.485 --> 01:52.445
<i>At last I lay down...</i>

01:55.115 --> 01:56.950
<i>What you got now, ass wipe?</i>

02:03.832 --> 02:05.125
<i>What the fuck?!</i>

02:05.166 --> 02:08.878
<i>Psycho.</i>

02:08.920 --> 02:12.423
<i>Fuck.</i>

02:15.510 --> 02:17.554
<i>Oh. Oh.</i>

02:19.013 --> 02:20.640
<i>Holy shit, man!</i>

02:20.682 --> 02:23.059
<i>You fucking killed him!</i>

02:23.101 --> 02:24.811
<i>Ah! No!</i>

02:37.490 --> 02:41.119
<i>And I'll cherish
the old rugged cross</i>

02:41.161 --> 02:44.330
<i>Old rugged cross</i>

02:44.372 --> 02:46.332
<i>Till my trophies</i>

02:46.374 --> 02:50.837
<i>At last I lay down</i>

02:50.879 --> 02:53.173
<i>Yes, I will cling</i>

02:53.214 --> 02:58.178
<i>To the old rugged cross</i>

02:58.219 --> 03:00.180
<i>And exchange it</i>

03:00.221 --> 03:04.893
<i>Some day for a crown...</i>

03:15.320 --> 03:18.364
<i>Who the hell is this guy?</i>

03:24.537 --> 03:26.706
<i>Afternoon, Mr. Caldwell.</i>

03:29.667 --> 03:32.212
<i>Hey, Elric,
could you turn the fucking</i>

03:32.253 --> 03:34.047
<i>hillbilly music down a little?</i>

03:34.088 --> 03:36.216
<i>Yeah. Sor-Sorry.</i>

03:36.257 --> 03:37.634
<i>The old ru...</i>

03:38.760 --> 03:40.887
<i>Everything okay?</i>

03:40.929 --> 03:42.722
<i>Yeah, everything's fine.</i>

03:42.764 --> 03:45.683
<i>Just checking in.
How's your job coming?</i>

03:45.725 --> 03:48.186
Oh, I got
your fish-and-game guy.

03:48.228 --> 03:50.355
<i>Oh, easy as pie.
You handling his son?</i>

03:50.396 --> 03:51.731
<i>My son?</i>

03:51.773 --> 03:53.191
<i>I'm handling everything.</i>

03:53.233 --> 03:54.609
<i>I'll see you soon.</i>

03:54.651 --> 03:57.070
<i>slow, suspenseful music</i>

04:46.619 --> 04:48.621
<i>up-tempo, dramatic music</i>

04:53.835 --> 04:57.046
<i>Fuck.</i>

05:03.594 --> 05:05.138
<i>Ah.</i>

05:12.979 --> 05:15.148
<i></i>

05:20.236 --> 05:22.322
<i>Fuck!</i>

05:50.391 --> 05:53.561
<i></i>

