<i>Hello?</i>

06:18.836 --> 06:22.548
<i>Hey, Harrison, I'm headed to
the Truck Stop. Are you there?</i>

06:22.590 --> 06:23.883
<i>I thought you were in jail.</i>

06:23.925 --> 06:25.134
<i>Oh, no, no, no.</i>

06:25.176 --> 06:26.511
<i>That... We got that cleared up.</i>

06:26.552 --> 06:27.887
<i>That was just
a misunderstanding.</i>

06:27.929 --> 06:29.680
<i>Cool. Cool.</i>

06:29.722 --> 06:31.682
<i>Y-Yeah, actually, I, um...</i>

06:31.724 --> 06:34.310
<i>I-I'm not at the Truck Stop</i>

06:34.352 --> 06:36.145
<i>right now. I had to leave
a little early, uh,</i>

06:36.187 --> 06:38.231
<i>'cause my dad came by,
we had a huge fight.</i>

06:38.272 --> 06:40.566
<i>What do you mean, a huge fight?
You okay?</i>

06:40.608 --> 06:42.068
<i>Yeah, I'm okay.</i>

06:42.110 --> 06:44.153
<i>Yeah, well,
it doesn't sound like it.</i>

06:44.195 --> 06:46.572
<i>Your dad just doesn't let up,
does he?</i>

06:47.532 --> 06:49.492
<i>Is he with you now?</i>

06:49.534 --> 06:52.537
<i>N-No, I, um...
I don't know where he is.</i>

06:52.578 --> 06:54.539
<i>Mm.</i>

06:54.580 --> 06:57.834
<i>Uh, well, did he call you
to check to see if you're okay?</i>

06:57.875 --> 07:00.253
<i>No.</i>

07:00.294 --> 07:04.632
<i>Okay. Well, I'm sure he's just,
uh, tied up with something.</i>

07:04.674 --> 07:08.052
<i>Hey, listen, buddy,
uh, where are you?</i>

07:08.094 --> 07:12.265
<i>Um, I'm a-across the street
from the-the Christmas tree lot.</i>

07:12.306 --> 07:14.308
<i>Okay, you stay right there,
all right?</i>

07:14.350 --> 07:17.019
<i>I'm gonna come and pick you up.</i>

07:17.061 --> 07:18.896
<i>I got a surprise for you.</i>

07:18.938 --> 07:20.606
<i>slow, ominous music</i>

07:41.669 --> 07:43.129
<i>I got to lose this guy,</i>

07:43.171 --> 07:45.965
<i>get back to his truck
and find my son.</i>

07:55.766 --> 07:58.269
<i>Hey. What's up?</i>

07:58.311 --> 07:59.812
<i>It's Christmas Eve is what's up.</i>

07:59.854 --> 08:01.647
<i>-Go home.</i>

08:01.689 --> 08:04.192
<i>Yeah. I'm...
I'm headed out soon.</i>

08:04.233 --> 08:07.361
<i>-You good?
- I will be.</i>

08:07.403 --> 08:09.822
<i>Well, you know,
if you ever, uh,</i>

08:09.864 --> 08:11.949
<i>want to grab a drink
or anything...</i>

08:13.326 --> 08:15.995
<i>...I'm sure that Jim would love
to hear from you.</i>

08:17.622 --> 08:19.290
<i>Did you hear that we-we had
drinks the other night?</i>

08:19.332 --> 08:20.666
<i>-I didn't.
- You know, he acts</i>

08:20.708 --> 08:22.752
<i>all easy breezy,
but underneath, he's...</i>

08:22.793 --> 08:24.295
<i>He cares a lot</i>

08:24.337 --> 08:26.839
<i>about you and Harrison.
I mean, look at how</i>

08:26.881 --> 08:28.508
<i>upset he got
after his kid almost OD'd.</i>

08:28.549 --> 08:30.384
<i>Nearly killed that drug dealer.</i>

08:30.426 --> 08:33.095
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

08:33.137 --> 08:35.473
<i>Uh, that's right.
You were, um...</i>

08:35.515 --> 08:39.810
<i>You were in New York.
Well, we went to Crystal Bar</i>

08:39.852 --> 08:42.522
<i>to arrest the drug dealer,
Miles O'Flynn.</i>

08:42.563 --> 08:44.941
<i>Jim had already found the guy</i>

08:44.982 --> 08:47.360
<i>and was, uh,
beating the shit out of him.</i>

08:47.401 --> 08:49.820
<i>-How did you not tell me this?
- Oh, I meant to. I just...</i>

08:49.862 --> 08:51.822
<i>Okay, look,
I didn't want it to look like</i>

08:51.864 --> 08:53.699
<i>I was talking shit
about your boyfriend.</i>

08:53.741 --> 08:55.952
<i>Uh, his anger got
the best of him.</i>

08:55.993 --> 08:58.955
<i>If-if it was my kid, I probably
would have reacted the same way.</i>

09:00.414 --> 09:02.583
<i>I'm sorry. I'm sorry.</i>

09:02.625 --> 09:04.585
<i>I-I-I wasn't trying to,
you know,</i>

09:04.627 --> 09:06.128
<i>make you upset or anything. I--</i>

09:06.170 --> 09:07.672
<i>Oh, it's okay. It's okay.</i>

09:07.713 --> 09:11.759
<i>It's... it's been a tough week.</i>

09:11.801 --> 09:13.761
<i>eerie, dramatic music</i>

09:34.156 --> 09:36.742
<i>[Dexter]</i> <i>I really hate it
when I'm the one who's bleeding.</i>

09:38.536 --> 09:40.496
<i>slow, suspenseful music</i>

09:51.048 --> 09:53.759
<i>Your son's blood.</i>

09:53.801 --> 09:56.637
<i>It's all on your hands.</i>

09:58.472 --> 10:00.433
<i>Goddamn save him.</i>

10:00.474 --> 10:03.311
<i>I'm working on it.</i>

10:10.818 --> 10:14.614
<i>That's it. I guarantee
it'll make you feel dyno-mite.</i>

10:15.239 --> 10:18.868
<i>-Shit. No, I wasn't doing shit!
- Hey! Hey, hey!</i>

10:18.909 --> 10:20.286
<i>You've got some time to talk.</i>

10:20.328 --> 10:22.747
<i>Fucking bullshit! I was just</i>

10:22.788 --> 10:24.749
<i>-drinking a beer, man.
- Relax, Miles.</i>

10:24.790 --> 10:26.917
<i>I'm not gonna hurt you
or bust you.</i>

10:26.959 --> 10:28.961
<i>I'm here to ask you about your
encounter with Jim Lindsay.</i>

10:29.003 --> 10:30.463
<i>Who?</i>

10:30.504 --> 10:31.839
<i>He was the guy
who did that to your face.</i>

10:31.881 --> 10:35.092
<i>Oh. That guy. Fucking lunatic.</i>

10:35.134 --> 10:37.136
<i>Yeah. I'm still thinking
about pressing charges.</i>

10:37.178 --> 10:39.096
<i>Do you want
to tell me what went down?</i>

10:39.138 --> 10:42.433
<i>This isn't like a trick
or something, right?</i>

10:42.475 --> 10:43.851
<i>Like, you're not trying
to entrap me?</i>

10:43.893 --> 10:45.811
<i>Okay?
'Cause I'm not fucking stupid.</i>

10:45.853 --> 10:50.775
<i>No? Well, you help me out,
I'll return the favor.</i>

10:50.816 --> 10:53.027
<i>Okay. All right.</i>

10:53.069 --> 10:57.031
<i>So, I was at the bar,
having a drink,</i>

10:57.073 --> 11:00.034
<i>when that, uh, Jim dude,
or whatever his name is,</i>

11:00.076 --> 11:01.786
<i>comes over to me,
all friendly and shit.</i>

11:01.827 --> 11:05.122
<i>-Friendly?
- Yeah. He asks me</i>

11:05.164 --> 11:08.250
<i>if I could... do him a favor.</i>

11:08.292 --> 11:10.503
<i>Heard you might know
where to get some blues.</i>

11:10.544 --> 11:12.755
<i>Follow me outside.</i>

11:12.797 --> 11:14.799
<i>He asked you for drugs?</i>

11:14.840 --> 11:16.926
<i>Your words, not mine.</i>

11:16.967 --> 11:19.929
<i>Anyway, so he gets me outside
over by the dumpsters.</i>

11:23.349 --> 11:24.642
<i>So I could...</i>

11:24.684 --> 11:26.811
<i>So you could do him that favor?</i>

11:26.852 --> 11:29.647
<i>Right. Except out of nowhere,
he fucking jumped me.</i>

11:29.689 --> 11:32.233
<i>He just started attacking you
with no provocation?</i>

11:32.274 --> 11:34.318
<i>Yeah, just started
swinging at me.</i>

11:34.360 --> 11:36.320
<i>And look, okay,
this is gonna sound crazy,</i>

11:36.362 --> 11:38.406
<i>but before he started
pounding on me,</i>

11:38.447 --> 11:41.033
<i>he poked me in the neck, with,
like, a needle or some shit.</i>

11:42.576 --> 11:44.870
<i>-A needle?
- Yeah, and so, I was like,</i>

11:44.912 --> 11:47.206
<i>"What the fuck?" And I look up,
and I see the police rolling up,</i>

11:47.248 --> 11:49.417
<i>and I'm like,
what the actual fuck?</i>

11:49.458 --> 11:51.502
<i>And that's when he started
throwing fists, man.</i>

11:53.379 --> 11:55.047
<i>-Wait. Wait.
- He's got fast hands, yo.</i>

11:55.089 --> 11:57.508
<i>He starts punching you
after the cops show up?</i>

11:57.550 --> 12:00.261
<i>Yeah, man. Yeah, just right
as they rolled up.</i>

12:00.302 --> 12:02.012
<i>And the thing he poked you with,
you're sure it was a needle?</i>

12:02.054 --> 12:04.056
<i>Well, I-I didn't really
get a good look at it, okay?</i>

12:04.098 --> 12:06.058
<i>It all happened so fast,
but, like, I mean, look.</i>

12:06.100 --> 12:09.311
<i>I still got the fucking mark.
Check it.</i>

12:34.378 --> 12:36.338
<i>Kurt said I had
to bring you in alive.</i>

12:36.380 --> 12:38.424
<i>You know what?</i>

12:38.466 --> 12:41.761
<i></i>

12:41.802 --> 12:44.930
<i>He'll just have to understand.</i>

12:47.433 --> 12:49.310
<i></i>

12:50.436 --> 12:53.105
<i>Right?</i>

12:53.147 --> 12:56.776
<i>I mean, you know, shit.</i>

13:02.740 --> 13:07.077
<i>I think the school's closed for,
you know, Christmas break.</i>

13:07.119 --> 13:09.079
<i>Yeah, well, they haven't
changed the locks</i>

13:09.121 --> 13:12.875
<i>since I was Matt's wrestling
coach, so...</i>

13:12.917 --> 13:14.460
<i>What about security cameras?</i>

13:14.502 --> 13:16.712
<i>Oh, you mean
for our precious children?</i>

13:16.754 --> 13:20.132
<i>No, those are reserved
for tracking white deer</i>

13:20.174 --> 13:22.426
<i>because that's what's important, right?</i>

13:22.468 --> 13:24.637
<i>Sometimes it feels good to be bad.</i>

13:24.678 --> 13:28.641
<i>Don't you think?</i>

13:28.682 --> 13:30.309
<i>Yeah.</i>

13:30.351 --> 13:34.480
<i>Besides, what are they gonna
do-- arrest me? Again?</i>

13:53.415 --> 13:55.000
<i>Fucking snow.</i>

13:55.042 --> 13:57.628
<i>Even a three-year-old
could track me.</i>

14:21.402 --> 14:23.529
<i>Come on, big man,
head on down that creek</i>

14:23.571 --> 14:25.865
<i>so I can get back to my son.</i>

14:31.245 --> 14:33.205
<i>First perfect game</i>

14:33.247 --> 14:35.374
<i>-in school history.
- That's Matt?</i>

14:35.416 --> 14:39.211
<i>Yeah. He was about your age.</i>

14:39.253 --> 14:41.630
<i>Ah, I used to go
to every one of his games.</i>

14:41.672 --> 14:44.550
<i>That's what I loved most
about being a dad.</i>

14:44.592 --> 14:49.179
<i>Whoa. He lettered
in three sports?</i>

14:49.221 --> 14:53.058
<i>Yeah. He was...</i>

14:53.100 --> 14:55.352
<i>he was special.</i>

14:55.394 --> 14:58.355
<i>Well, how's he doing?
Have you talked to him lately?</i>

14:58.397 --> 15:01.692
<i>Actually...
I haven't, you know.</i>

15:01.734 --> 15:03.819
<i>Uh, we never really
communicated very well.</i>

15:03.861 --> 15:05.613
<i>Not like you and me.</i>

15:05.654 --> 15:07.781
<i>Oh.</i>

15:09.533 --> 15:11.577
<i>Does that mean he's not
coming home for Christmas?</i>

15:11.619 --> 15:15.372
<i>Uh... you know,
with all the search party,</i>

15:15.414 --> 15:18.584
<i>I think he's afraid
to show his face around here.</i>

15:18.626 --> 15:21.420
<i>That's too bad.</i>

15:21.462 --> 15:22.838
<i>People are pretty forgiving.</i>

15:22.880 --> 15:25.299
<i>Especially during the holidays.</i>

15:26.717 --> 15:29.762
<i>Not everyone.</i>

15:29.803 --> 15:32.848
<i>Hey, let's go
have some fun, huh? Come on.</i>

15:44.485 --> 15:46.904
<i>Oldest trick
in the goddamn book.</i>

15:46.946 --> 15:48.781
<i>You want to play games?</i>

15:48.822 --> 15:51.450
<i>I can do this all fucking day.</i>

15:51.492 --> 15:54.495
<i>[Dexter]</i> <i>You might have
all day, but I don't.</i>

16:01.710 --> 16:05.172
<i>-Shit. This is great.
Yeah. Right?</i>

16:05.214 --> 16:07.216
<i>Small towns love them
some sport, huh?</i>

16:09.051 --> 16:11.345
<i>I mean, what else
we gonna do, right?</i>

16:11.387 --> 16:13.639
<i>Okay.</i>

16:17.309 --> 16:18.978
<i>Uh, let's see...</i>

16:19.019 --> 16:20.729
<i>That one...</i>

16:20.771 --> 16:22.314
<i>All right.</i>

