16:27.361 --> 16:28.696
<i>All right, wait for me
to get down there.</i>

16:28.737 --> 16:30.614
<i>Okay.</i>

16:36.954 --> 16:38.580
<i>Okay.</i>

16:40.207 --> 16:41.375
<i>All right, anytime.</i>

16:54.054 --> 16:56.265
<i>Whoa!</i>

16:56.306 --> 16:58.934
<i>Wow. Matt's got nothing
on you, huh?</i>

16:58.976 --> 17:00.269
<i>Yeah, well, I led
the Mountain League</i>

17:00.310 --> 17:01.854
<i>in batting my senior year.</i>

17:01.895 --> 17:04.732
<i>Taught him everything...</i>

17:04.773 --> 17:06.942
<i>he knows.
