17:12.322 --> 17:14.783
<i>You ever play?</i>

17:14.825 --> 17:17.578
<i>-What, Jim never taught you?
- No.</i>

17:19.163 --> 17:21.832
<i>All right.
Let's see what you got.</i>

17:34.011 --> 17:36.638
<i>Summer camp.</i>

17:36.680 --> 17:38.557
<i>Perfect place for
a serial killer</i>

17:38.599 --> 17:40.309
<i>to make his stand.</i>

17:43.729 --> 17:45.731
<i>All right. Batter up!</i>

17:48.442 --> 17:49.818
<i>Sorry.</i>

17:49.860 --> 17:51.028
<i>It's okay, you don't have
to apologize.</i>

17:51.070 --> 17:53.447
<i>Okay. Here you go.</i>

17:54.907 --> 17:57.409
<i>It's all right.</i>

17:57.451 --> 17:59.411
<i>You just weren't taught right.</i>

17:59.453 --> 18:02.748
<i>Y-You're swinging with
your wrists, all right?</i>

18:02.790 --> 18:04.291
<i>Good instincts,
but you've got to use</i>

18:04.333 --> 18:05.709
<i>your whole body, right?</i>

18:05.751 --> 18:08.545
<i>You've got to step
with your legs.</i>

18:08.587 --> 18:10.589
<i>Swing. Whole body.</i>

18:10.631 --> 18:12.591
<i>There you go. Good.
One more time.</i>

18:12.633 --> 18:14.843
<i>Step. Whole body.</i>

18:14.885 --> 18:17.638
<i>All right, now, this time,
step, whole body,</i>

18:17.679 --> 18:19.348
<i>snap your wrists. Ready?</i>

18:19.389 --> 18:21.683
<i>Step, whole body, snap!</i>

18:21.725 --> 18:23.852
<i>There you go. There.</i>

18:23.894 --> 18:26.355
<i>You're not afraid,
are you?</i>

18:26.396 --> 18:28.482
<i>-No.
- Good.</i>

18:35.948 --> 18:37.783
<i>Now...</i>

18:39.284 --> 18:40.786
<i>Ready?</i>

18:43.288 --> 18:46.083
<i>Okay. Just... relax.</i>

18:46.125 --> 18:48.961
<i>Keep your head down.
Eye on the ball, all right?</i>

18:49.002 --> 18:51.213
<i>- gentle music</i>
<i>-Ready?</i>

18:53.465 --> 18:56.301
<i>Hey, attaboy!
Attaboy. All right.</i>

18:56.343 --> 18:59.221
<i>Good, good, good.
Now, step into it.</i>

18:59.263 --> 19:01.140
<i>Oh!</i>

19:01.181 --> 19:04.768
<i>There we go.</i>

19:04.810 --> 19:08.105
<i>-Whew! Good God!</i>

19:08.147 --> 19:10.149
<i>This is getting
too easy for you.</i>

19:10.190 --> 19:11.608
<i>You know what?
Let's try a curve ball.</i>

19:11.650 --> 19:13.735
<i>See how you handle that.</i>

19:14.945 --> 19:16.321
<i>All right. Here we go.</i>

19:26.123 --> 19:27.666
<i>You okay?</i>

19:27.708 --> 19:29.418
<i>Yeah.</i>

19:29.459 --> 19:31.420
<i>Yeah. I'm-I'm good.</i>

19:31.461 --> 19:33.672
<i>All right.</i>

19:48.770 --> 19:50.522
<i>Okay.</i>

19:52.149 --> 19:53.275
<i>Turn it back on.</i>

20:08.332 --> 20:10.417
<i>Sorry. I'm not the guy
you're looking for.</i>

20:14.004 --> 20:16.548
<i>Put another one in.</i>

20:26.600 --> 20:28.560
<i>And my own dad thinks I'm what?</i>

20:28.602 --> 20:30.938
<i>A liar? An animal?</i>

20:32.105 --> 20:34.566
<i>Again.</i>

20:37.319 --> 20:39.613
<i>Again.</i>

20:44.159 --> 20:45.535
<i>Again.</i>

20:48.330 --> 20:49.873
<i></i>

20:49.915 --> 20:51.833
<i>Again!</i>

21:12.729 --> 21:17.025
<i>You are one tough fucking kid.</i>

21:17.067 --> 21:19.778
<i>So, you ever had venison?</i>

21:19.820 --> 21:21.780
<i>No, I-- No, I've never had it.</i>

21:21.822 --> 21:24.950
<i>Really? You mean the whole time
you've been here in Iron Lake,</i>

21:24.992 --> 21:27.577
<i>Jim hasn't cooked you up
some venison?</i>

21:27.619 --> 21:29.288
<i>Nope.</i>

21:29.329 --> 21:32.165
<i>Oh. I don't know what the hell
he's waiting for.</i>

21:32.207 --> 21:35.794
<i>Come on, we're gonna rectify
that situation right now.</i>

21:35.836 --> 21:38.797
<i>All right. Let's go.</i>

21:38.839 --> 21:41.925
<i>I also see some</i>

21:41.967 --> 21:45.262
<i>quality Scotch
in your future.</i>

22:14.166 --> 22:16.126
<i>ominous music</i>

22:30.557 --> 22:32.601
<i>[Harrison]</i> <i>I thought we were
headed to your place.</i>

22:32.642 --> 22:35.520
<i>We are. I have a cabin
out this way.</i>

22:35.562 --> 22:37.022
<i>Oh, cool.</i>

22:37.064 --> 22:38.357
<i>Yeah. I do all my hunting
out here.</i>

22:38.398 --> 22:41.068
<i>It's where I keep my venison.</i>

22:41.109 --> 22:43.028
<i>It's nice, you know.
To have a place you can go</i>

22:43.070 --> 22:46.156
<i>to get away, be yourself.</i>

22:47.532 --> 22:48.992
<i>Yeah.</i>

22:54.247 --> 22:56.208
<i>dramatic music</i>

23:02.923 --> 23:05.884
<i>[Dexter]</i> <i>Hope he's as drawn
to blood as I am.</i>

23:31.368 --> 23:33.537
<i>You said you had all day.</i>

23:33.578 --> 23:35.080
<i>Well, I've got news for you.</i>

23:35.122 --> 23:37.749
<i>The night is mine.</i>

23:44.256 --> 23:46.091
What's going on?
Everything okay?

23:46.133 --> 23:48.385
<i>Yeah. It's just...</i>

23:48.427 --> 23:49.928
<i>You know what?
You were right.</i>

23:49.970 --> 23:51.638
<i>I pushed everything aside
to deal with Iris.</i>

23:51.680 --> 23:53.432
<i>I want to close out
all our files.</i>

23:53.473 --> 23:55.559
<i>-Now?
- Yeah, I keep thinking about</i>

23:55.600 --> 23:58.270
<i>that story you told me
about the opioid bust.</i>

23:58.311 --> 23:59.729
<i>You mind bringing me up to speed
on that case?</i>

23:59.771 --> 24:02.899
<i>Okay, um,
once we arrested Miles,</i>

24:02.941 --> 24:04.776
<i>I got him to snitch on
his supplier.</i>

24:04.818 --> 24:06.987
<i>Piece of shit
named Jasper Hodge.</i>

24:07.028 --> 24:09.281
<i>I coordinated with the Staties
to make the arrest,</i>

24:09.322 --> 24:11.950
<i>-but we got there too late.
- It was too late?</i>

24:11.992 --> 24:13.410
<i>Yeah. When we went
to make the arrest,</i>

24:13.452 --> 24:16.496
<i>he was already dead.</i>

24:16.538 --> 24:18.415
<i>Accidentally OD'd
on his own product</i>

24:18.457 --> 24:20.208
<i>while he was pressing pills.</i>

24:20.250 --> 24:21.710
<i>How long had he been dead
when you found him?</i>

24:21.751 --> 24:24.629
<i>About an hour before
we got there.</i>

24:24.671 --> 24:29.301
<i>So... maybe Miles
tipped Jasper off</i>

24:29.342 --> 24:30.927
<i>that the police were coming?</i>

24:30.969 --> 24:33.472
<i>Maybe he OD'd because
he didn't want to spend</i>

24:33.513 --> 24:35.807
<i>-all those years in prison?
- I don't think so.</i>

24:35.849 --> 24:37.726
<i>I mean, when I brought Miles
and Jim into the station,</i>

24:37.767 --> 24:39.561
<i>Miles gave up Jasper quick.</i>

24:39.603 --> 24:41.104
<i>But we held Miles for 24 hours,</i>

24:41.146 --> 24:43.023
<i>and Jasper was dead in ten.</i>

24:44.524 --> 24:46.318
<i>How long did you keep Jim
in custody?</i>

24:46.359 --> 24:48.153
<i>No more than an hour. I mean,
I wasn't trying to punish him.</i>

24:48.195 --> 24:49.738
<i>I just wanted to make sure
he cooled off.</i>

24:52.115 --> 24:54.117
<i>ominous music</i>

25:46.753 --> 25:50.382
<i>Stupid motherfucker took
a knife to a gun fight.</i>

25:53.593 --> 25:56.346
<i>All right.</i>

25:56.388 --> 25:58.890
<i>Yeah. Okay.</i>

26:23.248 --> 26:25.208
<i>intense music</i>

26:44.728 --> 26:46.938
<i>Christ! Who the hell are you?</i>

26:46.980 --> 26:48.690
<i>Where does Kurt have my son?</i>

26:48.732 --> 26:52.193
<i>Fuck you!
<i>Okay. Okay. Okay.</i></i>

26:52.235 --> 26:55.614
<i>I think Kurt's got him
up in his cabin on Stern road.</i>

26:55.655 --> 26:58.450
<i>That's where I was to bring you.</i>

26:58.491 --> 27:00.952
<i>That's all I know.</i>

27:00.994 --> 27:04.414
<i>I was just doing my job.</i>

27:04.456 --> 27:06.791
<i>No-Nothing personal.</i>

27:11.796 --> 27:13.673
<i>We're talking about my son.</i>

27:13.715 --> 27:16.301
<i>There's nothing more personal
than that.</i>

28:21.574 --> 28:23.660
<i>Do you see this often?</i>

28:23.702 --> 28:25.745
<i>Fentanyl overdose?
Are you kidding?</i>

28:25.787 --> 28:27.831
<i>-By the guy making the pills.
- Eh, it happens.</i>

28:27.872 --> 28:31.126
<i>He had, um,
ketamine in his system, too.</i>

28:31.167 --> 28:32.669
<i>That could explain it.</i>

28:32.711 --> 28:34.754
<i>-Was it lethal drug interaction?
- No.</i>

28:34.796 --> 28:36.339
<i>A party drug.</i>

28:36.381 --> 28:38.049
<i>Probably took it to mellow out.</i>

28:38.091 --> 28:40.760
<i>-Made him sloppy.
- So, there's nothing to suggest</i>

28:40.802 --> 28:42.303
<i>that Jasper's death was
anything other</i>

28:42.345 --> 28:44.097
<i>than an accidental overdose?</i>

28:44.139 --> 28:46.224
<i>Well, not unless
someone put a gun to his head</i>

28:46.266 --> 28:47.559
<i>and made him snort a line.</i>

28:47.600 --> 28:49.894
<i>Just want to check
one more thing.</i>

29:01.614 --> 29:04.117
<i>-Fucking faster, Dex!
- I'm going as fast as I can.</i>

29:04.159 --> 29:06.035
<i>-Text him. Warn him.
- It's risky.</i>

29:06.077 --> 29:08.747
<i>-You have to let him know.
- I don't want to tip off Kurt.</i>

29:10.248 --> 29:12.834
<i>This is the good stuff.</i>

29:12.876 --> 29:17.046
<i>This is what they call
single malt Scotch whisky.</i>

29:17.088 --> 29:20.550
<i>Best there is.
Only kind I drink.</i>

29:20.592 --> 29:23.219
<i>-Thank you.
- Go ahead. Give it a shot.</i>

29:26.389 --> 29:28.558
<i>-Hmm?</i>

29:29.893 --> 29:33.271
<i>Ooh. That kind of tastes
like a Band-Aid.</i>

29:40.612 --> 29:42.822
<i>You want to put
some ice on that?</i>

29:42.864 --> 29:44.574
<i>No, I'm good.</i>

29:44.616 --> 29:46.576
<i>Mm.</i>

29:49.829 --> 29:53.166
<i>Got to stop doing that
to yourself, kid.</i>

29:53.208 --> 29:54.876
<i>I mean, look, I get it.</i>

29:54.918 --> 29:57.295
<i>I-I used to do stuff like that
when I was your age.</i>

29:57.337 --> 29:58.880
<i>But the sooner you stop
punishing yourself</i>

29:58.922 --> 30:02.217
<i>for whatever you think
is wrong with you...</i>

30:03.635 --> 30:06.137
<i>Look, all I'm trying
to say is that</i>

30:06.179 --> 30:07.639
<i>you are who you are.</i>

30:07.680 --> 30:10.767
<i>Find what gives you joy,
and you do that thing.</i>

30:10.809 --> 30:12.727
<i>No apologies.</i>

30:12.769 --> 30:17.065
<i>Whatever it is that brings you
pleasure in this world.</i>

30:17.106 --> 30:20.610
<i>How do you...</i>

30:20.652 --> 30:22.487
<i>H-How do you do that?</i>

30:22.529 --> 30:25.114
<i>You just... take the leap.</i>

30:27.200 --> 30:31.162
<i>Well, I have
worked up quite an appetite.</i>

30:31.204 --> 30:32.330
<i>How about you?</i>

30:32.372 --> 30:34.541
<i>Starving.</i>

30:48.179 --> 30:51.641
<i>Whoo! This is gonna be tasty.</i>

31:01.484 --> 31:03.695
<i>Uh, hey, I'm-I'm getting
a little cold.</i>

31:03.736 --> 31:05.530
<i>Where's the firewood
for the stove?</i>

31:05.572 --> 31:08.658
<i>Um, it's around the side of
the house. I'll get it.</i>

31:08.700 --> 31:09.951
<i>Oh, no, no, no. I got it.</i>

31:09.993 --> 31:13.538
<i>Come on, Harrison.
Come on. Come on.</i>

31:26.342 --> 31:27.969
<i>You good?</i>

31:28.011 --> 31:29.637
<i>Yeah.</i>

31:29.679 --> 31:31.890
<i>You know, if it's getting late
and you need to be home,</i>

31:31.931 --> 31:33.725
<i>I'm happy to give you a ride.</i>

31:33.766 --> 31:36.394
<i>No. No way.</i>

31:36.436 --> 31:38.104
<i>I wouldn't want to miss out
on all the venison.</i>

31:39.647 --> 31:42.233
<i>Yeah, it's smelling
pretty tasty in there.</i>

31:44.444 --> 31:45.695
<i>I'm glad we're doing this, kid.</i>

31:47.113 --> 31:48.907
<i>Me, too.</i>

31:48.948 --> 31:50.867
<i>All right. Hurry up.</i>

32:09.886 --> 32:12.013
<i>Shit.</i>

32:12.055 --> 32:15.183
<i>So I'm trying to make weight.</i>

32:15.224 --> 32:19.437
<i>And I-- you know. I start
wearing a-a garbage bag, right?</i>

32:19.479 --> 32:21.105
<i>-Mm-hmm.
- And then go for a run.</i>

32:21.147 --> 32:24.192
<i>I'm drenched in sweat,
I got terrible BO,</i>

32:24.233 --> 32:27.195
<i>and I'm wearing
a frigging Hefty bag.</i>

32:27.236 --> 32:28.696
<i>-Mm.
- I run around the corner,</i>

32:28.738 --> 32:30.740
<i>and there she is,</i>

32:30.782 --> 32:33.076
<i>-walking her dog.
- Oh, man.</i>

32:33.117 --> 32:35.787
<i>I had been gearing up</i>

32:35.828 --> 32:38.456
<i>to ask her to the Spring Dance
all week,</i>

32:38.498 --> 32:41.000
<i>but, you know, at school,
there's always people around,</i>

32:41.042 --> 32:43.628
<i>and I... I don't know.
I just kept pussying out.</i>

32:43.670 --> 32:44.963
<i>-I get it.
- So, this time,</i>

32:45.004 --> 32:46.422
<i>I say, "Okay, forget about it."</i>

32:46.464 --> 32:48.174
<i>I'm-I'm gonna take my shot.</i>

32:48.216 --> 32:50.134
<i>I'm gonna, I'm gonna ask her.
Right there, right then.</i>

32:50.176 --> 32:52.470
<i>What'd she say?</i>

32:52.512 --> 32:55.431
<i>Well, she looked me
up and down,</i>

32:55.473 --> 32:58.977
<i>like I had just escaped
from a mental ward, and said,</i>

32:59.018 --> 33:02.271
<i>"Do I look like I date
white trash?"</i>

33:06.025 --> 33:08.069
<i>Just laid me out.</i>

33:08.111 --> 33:10.363
<i>But you probably don't have
that problem.</i>

33:10.405 --> 33:13.783
<i>You're going out with the police
chief's daughter, right?</i>

33:13.825 --> 33:17.412
<i>Uh, I don't know.
After that last wrestling match,</i>

33:17.453 --> 33:20.456
<i>I-I think she looks at me like
I just escaped a mental ward.</i>

33:20.498 --> 33:23.626
<i>Well, you know, I guess some
people are just never</i>

33:23.668 --> 33:26.504
<i>gonna understand guys
like you and me.</i>

33:28.131 --> 33:29.924
<i>You know what I say?</i>

33:29.966 --> 33:31.843
<i>Fuck 'em.</i>

33:31.884 --> 33:33.928
<i>-Yeah.</i>

33:33.970 --> 33:36.139
<i>-Fuck 'em!
- Fuck 'em!</i>

33:36.180 --> 33:38.891
<i>Attaboy.</i>

33:41.185 --> 33:42.353
<i>Ah.</i>

33:45.857 --> 33:50.361
<i>So... so-so what happened
with you going to jail?</i>

33:50.403 --> 33:52.905
<i>W-What was that about?</i>

33:52.947 --> 33:56.200
<i>Well, it was...</i>

33:56.242 --> 33:58.161
<i>just a little mix-up
with some DNA.</i>

33:58.202 --> 34:01.956
<i>Well, it turns out
that my dad</i>

34:01.998 --> 34:06.878
<i>murdered a teenage girl
in Iron Lake 25 years ago.</i>

34:06.919 --> 34:09.005
<i>-Oh, shit.
- Yeah.</i>

34:10.923 --> 34:13.926
<i>He was a really messed up guy.</i>

34:13.968 --> 34:17.805
<i>Wasn't easy growing up being
his son, I can tell you that.</i>

34:17.847 --> 34:20.224
<i>And I guess, you know,
since I spent the night</i>

34:20.266 --> 34:23.061
<i>in jail because of him,
it still isn't easy.</i>

34:24.103 --> 34:26.355
<i>Eh, you know.</i>

34:26.397 --> 34:28.983
<i>Sometimes a kid
just ends up suffering</i>

34:29.025 --> 34:32.904
<i>for the...
choices of his father.</i>

34:35.364 --> 34:38.576
<i>So, hey, why did the dad that</i>

34:38.618 --> 34:40.912
<i>abandoned you for ten years</i>

34:40.953 --> 34:45.541
<i>end up getting in a fight
with you at my truck stop?</i>

34:45.583 --> 34:48.586
<i>Oh, I-I don't even know
if it was a fight</i>

34:48.628 --> 34:50.922
<i>as much it was just me</i>

34:50.963 --> 34:53.549
<i>being pissed at him</i>

34:53.591 --> 34:55.927
<i>-all the time.
- Ah.</i>

34:55.968 --> 35:00.723
<i>I just feel like I keep wanting
something from him that...</i>

35:02.850 --> 35:06.145
<i>What? What do you want, kid?</i>

35:06.187 --> 35:08.356
<i>I don't know. I...</i>

35:08.397 --> 35:11.776
<i>When I came here,
I wanted answers.</i>

35:11.818 --> 35:14.028
<i>A-And now, as much as I...</i>

35:14.070 --> 35:17.782
<i>fucking hate to say it...</i>

35:17.824 --> 35:19.575
<i>I-I think I was also</i>

35:19.617 --> 35:23.788
<i>looking for, you know...</i>

35:24.413 --> 35:28.292
<i>Connection. Real connection
with your dad. Hmm?</i>

35:30.128 --> 35:31.629
<i>Yeah.</i>

35:35.258 --> 35:37.051
<i>But I-I think he knew.</i>

35:37.093 --> 35:38.219
<i>Even when I was five,</i>

35:38.261 --> 35:40.304
<i>I think, I think he knew</i>

35:40.346 --> 35:42.640
<i>how different we were.</i>

35:42.682 --> 35:45.977
<i>Yo, this is Harrison. Leave a
message and I'll hit you back.</i>

35:49.021 --> 35:51.649
<i>Well, w-we don't get
each other on, like,</i>

35:51.691 --> 35:56.237
<i>a-a normal,
father-son level.</i>

35:56.279 --> 36:00.783
<i>I-I feel like he's always
holding something back from me,</i>

36:00.825 --> 36:03.244
<i>or... I don't know.</i>

36:03.286 --> 36:06.831
<i>Whatever blood-bond most fathers
have with their kids,</i>

36:06.873 --> 36:10.001
it's-it's not there.

36:10.042 --> 36:13.546
<i>Listen to me. You cannot
blame yourself for that.</i>

36:13.588 --> 36:15.173
<i>That is on him.</i>

36:16.132 --> 36:17.675
<i>Yeah.</i>

36:17.717 --> 36:20.094
<i>Maybe it's his
childhood abandonment shit.</i>

36:20.136 --> 36:21.971
<i>Maybe it's mine.</i>

36:23.347 --> 36:26.184
<i>E-Either way,
I got my answer.</i>

36:31.731 --> 36:33.566
<i>If you were my son,</i>

36:33.608 --> 36:36.235
<i>I would never have
walked out on you.</i>

36:37.236 --> 36:38.905
<i>Ever.</i>

36:42.575 --> 36:45.703
<i>-Tha-Thank you for saying that.
- I mean it.</i>

36:51.876 --> 36:55.671
<i>-Ah, damn.
- What's up?</i>

36:55.713 --> 36:57.465
<i>Uh...</i>

36:57.506 --> 37:00.176
<i>Just something I have to
take care of.</i>

37:00.218 --> 37:02.386
<i>Okay. I'll be right back.</i>

37:25.034 --> 37:28.329
<i>intense music</i>

37:30.581 --> 37:33.042
<i>W-What are you doing?</i>

37:36.837 --> 37:38.506
<i>Wish it could've worked out
differently.</i>

37:38.547 --> 37:40.341
<i>But I don't have a choice, son.</i>

37:40.383 --> 37:42.593
<i>Sins of the father.</i>

37:42.635 --> 37:45.721
<i>It's a fucked-up world
out there.</i>

37:45.763 --> 37:47.848
<i>-I-I don't...
- Get up.</i>

37:50.226 --> 37:52.103
<i>Get out.</i>

37:55.314 --> 37:57.692
What-what-what,
did I say something wrong?

37:57.733 --> 38:00.444
<i>Did I do something?
